text.tspan: STEP ONE: Following Registration, you will land on your User Profile,
where you will be asked to link your account to Dwolla
Demo: After being redirected to Dwolla, select ‘Log In’ and enter the
following credentials
Username/Email: raft.fireflies@gmail.com
Password: AKAsquad4
From here you can create a Raft -
A group of friends that plan events
together - Invite your friends as fellow raft riders -
Create a poll to send out to friends, to decide on the when
& where of your next event!
When all of the members of your raft
vsubmitted a response to the event poll
the final event details are set.
Join Event to let your friends know your
coming.
Just remember your word is bond...
If you RSVP and fail to show, the event
organizer can “Send a Bill” to charge you for
for the inconvenience!
Raft is a social event planning
application. We aim take the stress
of finalizing event details off of the
event organizer, and make event
planning collaborative and just...easier!
